{"tid":1509543,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"泛民正準備出賣港人及抗爭者","createTime":"2019-08-27T01:17:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T04:57:16.000Z","uid":73092,"like":9,"dislike":123,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"ebd286af9aa3c206dcd6bd078e75383f4f63336c","tid":1509543,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T01:17:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V2y44tX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV2y44tX.jpg&h=8696b784&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d7a334215d844193a67faea38e4d785612fd7f51","tid":1509543,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T01:18:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hjf7rg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hjf7rg.gif&h=994c84f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrrQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=1244e732\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrrQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=7b44b29e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrrQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=8c445f5b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"f7cccdce69d86e08c680febb2d33f6858b480780","tid":1509543,"uid":48083,"like":18,"dislike":4,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T01:19:17.000Z","msg":"抺黑post勿推<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首先在此清楚表明，公民黨 Civic Party非常支持亦希望《香港民主與人權法案》能夠獲得通過，讓打壓、損害香港人權的官員需為他們的行為「後果自負」，受到限制入境、資產凍結等等制裁。<br />\n<br />\n在7月13日我已經在Facebook呼籲大家簽白宮聯署，要求美國國會通過《香港人權與民主法案》，今次旅程就是以香港人的身份，將香港反送中運動的實況帶到美國。<br />\n<br />\n[正視聽] 涂謹申、楊岳橋、郭榮鏗同葉建源走咗去美國支持《香港人權與民主法案》<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1509449\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1509449</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"efa79f4d8525a1a15bf1caea247c3ab7a905a6dd","tid":1509543,"uid":264891,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T01:19:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea7525d1d7f128a42f152e1306b7977c54e80650","tid":1509543,"uid":301820,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T01:20:45.000Z","msg":"泛民死開啦"},{"pid":"40bade22efee7107f407f1f1943ccfb8a61e3e63","tid":1509543,"uid":35842,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T01:20:48.000Z","msg":"小知識 - 原來機場控制唔只控制香港D機上落，<br />\n廣洲，深圳，澳門既飛機升降都會受香港指揮影響，搞到D飛升降唔到。。。。<br />\n大家千祈唔好搞到機場控制個班番唔到工啊 會好大獲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n現有文宣集合 (Google Drive)<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrrQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=b9151106\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2</a><br />\n請隨便使用，用自己的方法幫忙發送文宣出去，感謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LoOsXdt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F