dBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T01:21:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4436272a76a323110b821e4f6adf2efaf7f6b5d1","tid":1509543,"uid":63757,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T01:22:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">抹黑撚收皮啦</span>"},{"pid":"6ea233c6d9995c65a3866a4c39081763e1fba93e","tid":1509543,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T01:23:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d41315c22a0f3c205beb150cd4780313c3156573","tid":1509543,"uid":3820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T01:23:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d93b2de2af94aad8800c812807f770ffab4cbe88","tid":1509543,"uid":171866,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T01:23:59.000Z","msg":"仲搞分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8915a413cfc9641bbf16e96a7566b03bc25cc97","tid":1509543,"uid":87672,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T01:24:04.000Z","msg":"收皮啦三毛，係美國兩邊嘅人都邀請過去<br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】民主派4名立法會議員民主黨涂謹申、教育界葉建源、公民黨郭榮鏗及楊岳橋，本月19至22日將應美國國務院邀請前往蒙大拿州，參與首次舉行的《香港-美國立法機關交流團》。郭榮鏗說，立法會原有8名議員獲邀，但建制派僅新民黨葉劉淑儀和自由黨鍾國斌參加，民建聯李慧琼和建制派「班長」廖長江不參與。郭強調此行是向國際社會講清楚香港正確的事實。楊岳橋揶揄有建制派放棄為《逃犯條例》修例「搖旗吶喊」，支持特首、香港警隊，又稱說民主派勾結外國勢力是「莫須有」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20190813/s00001/1565635191581/%E7%AB%8B%E6%9C%836%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E5%B0%87%E8%A8%AA%E7%BE%8E-%E6%B3%9B%E6%B0%91-%E8%AC%9B%E4%BA%8B%E5%AF%A6%E4%B8%8D%E6%B8%B8%E8%AA%AA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190813%2Fs00001%2F1565635191581%2F%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%259C%25836%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5