sfyvnaGYCnWTZZexflzPGmI1v0va5fenTY7YPsYTj06BIJh1bL-yEXul7KuixuVL6PbKIhgxOI3WsRVzmYh62xwnhM5j1Qhmzm7yOJqNy639PJjyHh2Mts6Zg0itGDrSGN791TWAQib4GUKM305C1dEOYloUF-uk4bGjSw9sjRrS4HTr2sF1YO5zIqKHt3RQtjNln7ppq90TOQ0GVROmH2PDFleVQJIZUoVCgdB7G_0rhmFh0uUIV7AJGkc8BJA9O1J39S8PvdJxIg[/img]</a><br />\n【官員賣港 後果自負】支持《香港人權與民主法案》<br />\n<br />\n臨上機前留意到網民很關心我和Dennis Kwok 郭榮鏗是否支持美國國會即將審議的《香港民主與人權法案2019》，亦留意到葉劉指與泛民有「共識」的問題。<br />\n<br />\n首先在此清楚表明，公民黨 Civic Party非常支持亦希望《香港民主與人權法案》能夠獲得通過，讓打壓、損害香港人權的官員需為他們的行為「後果自負」，受到限制入境、資產凍結等等制裁。<br />\n<br />\n在7月13日我已經在Facebook呼籲大家簽白宮聯署，要求美國國會通過《香港人權與民主法案》，今次旅程就是以香港人的身份，將香港反送中運動的實況帶到美國。<br />\n<br />\n我們帶了過去兩個月警察濫用暴力造成人道災難的照片作輔助解說，向美國各界說明香港人的五大訴求，讓他們更清楚了解香港的示威者並非暴徒，香港人只是透過不同的手法對抗警暴、要求政府回應訴求。<br />\n<br />\n最後，回應葉劉所謂的「共識」：從來沒有。<br />\n<br />\n#五大訴求缺一不可<br />\n#香港人加油"},{"pid":"f62a9059ea291e4ed23a458ac2e3a5511169a370","tid":1509543,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2d395909b7634e9df92023669f859765f1966ea5","tid":1509543,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"4436272a76a323110b821e4f6adf2efaf7f6b5d1","tid":1509543,"uid":63757,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T01:22:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">抹黑撚收皮啦</span>"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T01:24:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CHT8MKv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCHT8MKv.jpg&h=7f8066c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n泛民反對攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T01:28:02.000Z","msg":"葉劉反對<br />\n飯民支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c16c950499be814e843e456cc0248d4829ba8829","tid":1509543,"uid":31174,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T01:29:53.000Z","msg":"Fake news 分化post 收皮啦"},{"pid":"